Determine whether this social media post from Donald Trump contains a personal insult to Kamala Harris's intelligence. Simply return "yes" or "no".
content: Rep. ByronDonalds: "Inflation when Donald Trump left office was 1.4% year-over-year...When Joe Biden and Kamala Harris came into office, many states were already back to work...and when they wanted to his 'American Rescue Plan,' which she co-signed, we told them on Capitol Hill, you're going to create a labor shortage, which is going to create inflation."
